Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.74,0:00:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Rarity? How much\Nlonger are you planning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay in here, darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear, is somepony\Nelse waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.54,0:00:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I just don't\Nwant you to get all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,what is word, pruney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.32,0:00:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Well, I'm just waiting for\NApplejack. It's been so long
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,since we've had a relaxing\Nday at the spa together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.94,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite certain she'll be\Nalong any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, there, Rarity. I really\Ntried to get here earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't believe how\Nmuch time my chores
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.36,0:00:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,are taking up these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.64,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At least now we'll\Nfinally get to spend some
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.80,0:00:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,quality spa time\Ntogether, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,OK fillies, that's it. We're\Nclosing up for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.08,0:01:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks, Rarity. I guess\NI missed the whole day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I sure am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.04,0:01:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.14,0:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Regular subtitles\Nby YayPonies\NWe have muffins!\Nhttps://yp1.yayponies.no/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Twilight. Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.10,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good heavens that's a\Nlot of empty pie plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.62,0:02:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yeah. We were just heading\Nto pick up some fresh pies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.20,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why we keep\Nrunning out at the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you\Ngoing to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack,\Nactually.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I'm quite sure\Nshe'll be too busy once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.70,0:02:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing. It's just\Nthat Applejack and I
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.38,0:02:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't had one of our\Nspa days in ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You two really should set\Naside some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, I have been\Ntrying for moons,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but Applejack is so busy these\Ndays, it's next to impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. I didn't realize Applejack\Nhad so much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Applejack. Another\Norder of pies, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure thing, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't suppose those\Npies are the last chore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,on the schedule for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.71,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Gah! Land sakes! Is it time\Nfor our spa day already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.92,0:03:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, why don't you go on\Nahead and I'll meet you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Please, Applejack,\Nlet's not kid ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it ain't 'cause\NI don't wanna,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,but the work on the farm\Nhas just been taking up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,more and more of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.64,0:03:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate seeing you two not\Nspending time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you get somepony\Nelse in your family
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to take over for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wish I could, but Granny,\NBig Mac and Apple Bloom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,all have chores of their own\Nand today they're all busy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,taking the harvest\Nto market.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we're not farmers,\Nbut I'm sure Spike and I
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,could handle things\Nfor a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.42,0:03:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.16,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there one chore\Nwe could do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...I suppose if\Nyou two got started
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on feeding the pigs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I could maybe leave\Nfor an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.62,0:03:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,An hour of\Nspa perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I can work with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.78,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect. You head\Noff to the spa
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:03:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and Spike and I will take\Ncare of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.88,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Ugh! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh yeah. We've totally\Ngot everything covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.01,0:04:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. This list pretty\Nmuch covers everything
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to know\Nto feed the pigs,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,but uh, maybe I should go\Nover it with you just to--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, please, if\Nthere's a list involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am one hundred\Npercent on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And don't worry\Nabout things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike and I have\Ntotally got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.36,0:04:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, it's just feeding\Nthe pigs. How hard can it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad we're\Ndoing this, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been putting work before\Nour spa time for too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know we've only\Ngot an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.78,0:04:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't wait\Nto have a steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A steam is just\Nthe start.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I know exactly\Nwhat we'll do
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and an hour will\Nbe simply perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Spike. Ready\Nwith that list?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Step one, open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Step two, close the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.84,0:05:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. That's what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Step three, walk away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Walk away? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope Twilight and\NSpike can handle things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,until I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.69,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Applejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,if we are really to enjoy\Nthis time together,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you simply must give\Nyourself over to the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are off duty\Nand try to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. You're right. I really\Nam glad we're doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And as long as\Nit's only an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure everything\Nwill be just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Now, kindly step\Nthis way. Relaxation awaits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash?\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I didn't think\Nspa treatments
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,were your thing exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.90,0:06:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. They're totally not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,At least, not the\N"frou-frou" kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I-uh, I think\NI tweaked something
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,at Wonderbolts practice\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.26,0:06:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just came in for a deep\Ntissue sports massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Dash? I\Nam so sorry,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,but we are running\Njust a tad behind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and we're not quite\Nready to start your
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,pampered muzzle massage and\Nindulgent hooficure just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.92,0:06:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm pretty sure that\Nwasn't what I signed up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But they are your usuals-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like you're\Nreally busy today anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just come back tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, see you two\Nlater. Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But put me down for\Nthe same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.62,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad Rainbow\NDash just "hates" those
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"frou-frou" spa treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She could have joined\Nus for a nice steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo wee! I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed. Although if\Nthey couldn't fit Dashie in,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder just how far\Nbehind things are running.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously we're on a\Nvery tight schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.82,0:07:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe not everypony is\Nwaiting for the steam room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, that's exactly\Nwhat we're waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hope you're\Nnot in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So every pony here\Nwants a steam bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the solution\Nis obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll simply have to start\Nour short time at the spa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,with something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh! Nothin' doin'! I\Ncame here to have a steam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's just\Nwhat I'm gonna get.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.34,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But-but it will take\Nmost of our hour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get through\Nthis line.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.34,0:08:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! My favorite\Ncustomer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And Appleyack!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.90,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it certainly has been\Na long time since you two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,were here together. So\Nlovely to have you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wish I\Ncould say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the wait time\Nfor the steam room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly has been\Ngetting worse lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure we'll be\Nable to accommodate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.72,0:08:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,your usual treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not without my steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Applejack won't\Nconsider starting her time
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.96,0:08:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,at the spa without a steam\Nand we only have an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.38,0:08:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Why are y'all\Njust standing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Just waiting for\Nthe steam to build up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Without steam, a steam\Nroom's just a room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've got plenty\Nof those at home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.26,0:08:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because I live in a mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been taking longer\Nfor the steam to reach that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ponyville Day Spa" quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We even had to add a\Nwarm towel service.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry for the\Ndelay, everypony,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,please help yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if you're not\Ngetting enough steam,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.86,0:09:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that must mean there's\Nnot enough hot water.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Applejack, honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.18,0:09:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can't we just start\Nwith a hooficure?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to\Nrun out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! Now, what do we have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The laundry room, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And at this point, I'm\Nconsidering soaking my hooves
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,in one of the machines so my\Ntime here isn't a total loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.38,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The Ponyville Day Spa prides\Nitself on sanitary conditions
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and fresh linens\Nare integral part.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sure, but have you\Nalways run every single one
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of these here machines\Nfull-bore, all day, every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.34,0:10:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...but ponies sure do love\Ntheir warm towel service.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all wanting towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks to me like you\Ndon't have any left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, like I said. Warm\Ntowels are big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.90,0:11:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I figured\Nout the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a small leak\Nand that means the steam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,takes just a little\Nlonger to build up
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.50,0:11:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and while ponies wait,\Nthey get cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.34,0:11:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Cold ponies start wrapping\Nthemselves in towels...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...and all those dirty\Ntowels have to be cleaned...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...because Ponyville Day Spa\Nprides itself on cleanliness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.84,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Basically, losing steam\Nmakes you use more towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you do more laundry\Nwhich uses up the hot water
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to make more\Nsteam so the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,just keeps getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.38,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.That makes sense. I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.78,0:12:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've solved\Nthe great steam mystery,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,we can finally get\Nback to our...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,significantly less than\Nan hour of relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, are you kiddin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.08,0:12:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't just leave\Nthings like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna need my tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoo! Now that\Nthat leak's fixed,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ponies won't get so cold
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,they use up all those towels\Nand without all that laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,there'll be plenty of hot\Nwater for all the steam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.42,0:13:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,anypony could want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.02,0:13:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll only have to be\Ndoing wash once a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, Appleyack. Have you ever\Nconsidered a career
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.24,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,in the spa industry? I'm sure\NI can find something for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.48,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks. I'm just\Nrelieved I can finally relax
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.78,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in the steam. What do\Nyou say, Rarity?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm. It sounds lovely,\NApplejack,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.74,0:13:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...you spent so much time\Nfixing the steam room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have any time\Nleft to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, how in Equestria\Ndid it never occur to you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.20,0:13:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to check for leaks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's just so many other\Nthings to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.90,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we get used\Nto the way things are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and we don't realize\Nthere was problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You obviously need an outside\Neye to evaluate the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lucky for you Applejack\Nis too stubborn to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm sorry, Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll just have to\Ndo this another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight and Spike should be\Ndone feeding the pigs by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.54,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight is a very capable pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she can figure\Nout what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, I know Twilight's a\Nprincess and an alicorn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,but she isn't a farmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing farm work my\Nwhole life and I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it's something you\Ncan just figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.12,0:14:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. Why don't\Nwe pop back so you can explain
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to Twilight what to do next\Nand then we'll come back here
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and pick up where we left off?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.46,0:14:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose I could try,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,assuming everything\Nwent well so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Applejack, honestly!\NHow could it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.50,0:14:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be\Neasier to just fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.66,0:14:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, Spike, we're\Nfollowing Applejack's list
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to the letter and Applejack\Ndoesn't fly--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Rarity,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,but I think I'm gonna have to\Nfinish these chores myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, darling, how in the\Nworld did you end up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Spike and I were just trying\Nto follow Applejack's list
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,as closely as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.06,0:15:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm...maybe not the best plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Applejack.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never even got\Nstarted feeding the pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right, Twilight.\NI know you did your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.46,0:15:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess a list can't really\Ncapture all the ways I have
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,of doin' things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you two got to spend\Nsome time at the spa together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that must have\Nbeen super relaxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.52,0:15:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if watching\NApplejack fix plumbing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,counts as relaxing, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What about your hour\Nof spa perfection?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As it turns out, the Ponyville\NDay Spa had a few problems
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.04,0:16:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with their steam room and\Nsomepony refused to relax
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.74,0:16:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,until she had fixed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.34,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I just\Ncouldn't let those spa ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,go another minute putting\Nup with problems
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they didn't even know they had.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.56,0:16:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow they just got used to\Na huge bottleneck of ponies
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.42,0:16:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,standin' around waitin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But I took one good\Nlook at that spa-jam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I knew I had\Nto do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes the simplest\Nthings can just derail
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's a leaky pipe\Nor doing too much laundry,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't just stick to the\Nsame old way of doing things
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and expect them to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, thinking you can is\Njust plum ridiculous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.30,0:16:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's funny when\Nyou realize the extra work
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,they were doing was actually\Nmaking things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I guess it's possible\Nto get stuck in a routine
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,where you're doing all\Nthis extra stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and not realize it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.28,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't for the life\Nof me think of how.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.68,0:17:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are y'all starin'\Nat me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.40,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you certain\Neverything you just did
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,is entirely necessary\Nto feed the pigs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Of course! Why would\NI be doin' it if it weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,See this gate here used\Nto squeak so loud,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the pigs would run to the\Nother side of the pen
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and never come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,so I open and close it to\Nlet them know it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.08,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't squeak anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. I\Nfixed that ages ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.22,0:17:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I realized putting a\Nlittle fright into 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.02,0:17:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,got them all hustlin'\Nout of the pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't look\Nscared to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no, they got\Nused to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why I started doing\Nthe chicken dance to show 'em
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.94,0:17:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that if they didn't get to\Neatin' their food,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the chickens would.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, being a chicken,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't very\Nwell open the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting the food bucket to\Nspill into the trough
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,was just a happy accident
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.76,0:18:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,because one time I left\Nit there by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.62,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh Applejack, it seems like\Neverything you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is to fix things that aren't\Nreally problems anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. Maybe it isn't so\Nhard to get stuck
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,doing extra work after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, I wonder if I've been\Ndoing that around here
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's only\None way to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks y'all. I\Nguess I just got so used
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to doing everything\Na certain way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.88,0:20:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't realize there\Nwere any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Having a friend look\Nat what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with an outside eye\Ncan really help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.60,0:20:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Um-hm. And I suppose\Nif it weren't for our
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.88,0:20:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,unsuccessful time at the spa,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.64,0:20:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,none of us would\Nhave realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.82,0:20:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now that your\Nchores are streamlined,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you going to do\Nwith all the extra time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I have a few ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Think you can come\Nup with enough things
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.54,0:20:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to do now that we have\Nmore time to relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.18,0:20:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, I could plan a\Nweek's worth of treatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Well, let's\Njust start with the
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.86,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,rest of the day for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After all the work we\Njust did on the farm,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am ready for some\Nserious relaxation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for letting me\Nknow there was an opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I could\Nmake it without my
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,pampered muzzle massage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.64,0:20:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall I put you down for\Nanother one tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes a girl just has to\Npamper herself, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0}\N{\i1}certainly are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Oh! Hey! I\Nwas just, uh, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.06,0:21:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Getting a "sports"\Npamperin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't\Nworry, Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.36,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just heading in for\Nsome pampering ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.76,0:21:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You could always join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That is if you don't mind\Nsuffering through
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,one or two "frou-frou"\Ntreatments.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I suppose I could take\Nit. You know, for you ponies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Busted!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
